summary: Adds a trade post near the border to High Rock!
descriptionHtml:
Version 0.2: Added walls, tavern and an market. You can rent a room in the tavern and buy some stuff in the market.

NOTE: Far from finished, just wan\'t to know what you guys think about the idea.  No merchants or stuff like that added yet. 
Location: West of Northwatch keep. 

I need help with quests. If you can help me, please send me a message :)
